{"tid":1214901,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"打打下機畀手下推翻...","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:55:00.000Z","uid":21501,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8747d317a183b4c06a485a9f10f870c7e6fb63","tid":1214901,"uid":21501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:34:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近朋友叫我打隻營運類遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（唔開名，驚畀人話曲線宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n隻game自由度幾高，連請咩人嘅學歷同薪水都有得set<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後我就將班大學生推晒去做醫生律師，班mk就去做士兵維穩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人工方面，隻game話人工愈高，忠誠度愈高，咁我馬上set班士兵人工去到最高，大約一個月最低都$2600USD左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且每年加薪5%添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />班契弟仲唔擁護我做萬世皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後無論我推啲咩惡法，就算街上班市民幾多人都好，都會畀我啲+99武器打走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（話說班士兵好撚癲，用手榴彈速度仲快過我打cs用AK掃一排彈嘅速度。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我今日都如常login，仆佢個街，我比班忠誠度99嘅士兵推翻咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（btw click落去見到叛軍名單除咗士兵，仲有兒童節目主持，矮仔，同一個平時好鐘意刷我鞋嘅演員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)[member][/ <br />\nmember] 我個角色依家逃亡緊，不過去到邊都畀當地難民打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我嬲起上嚟，將部iPhone掟落地 成個moon爆咗 <br />\n<br />\n所以我想下各位巴打 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知唔知邊度整番個moon好 <br />\n<br />\nTHX"},{"pid":"a582410cd9fd902e964a44225519b3777f14a343","tid":1214901,"uid":149844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"10/10<br />\nbtw<br />\n呼籲各大市民即日開始行街見到警犬就噓佢<br />\n屌多兩句老母都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12217301321289fe35974ac838b9eb82ee5309db","tid":1214901,"uid":99607,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on99兜咁撚大個圈 大圈仔"}]}